Project Modules

This project has declared the following modules:

NameDescription
WSIT Build Tools CoreProvides common classes used by both wsit-ant-tasks and wsit-maven-plugin.
WSIT Maven MojoProvides maven goals for generating WSIT client and server side configuration.
WSIT Maven Mojo Integration TestsIntegration tests of WSIT Maven Mojo.
WSIT Ant TasksProvides ant tasks for generating WSIT client and server side configuration.
